                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18281023-204-off1189 t18281023-204-cd1190"></join>, 1 handkerchief, value 1s. 3d., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18281023-204-victim1066" type="victimName">
                        George 
